      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GOOSEBUMPS RICO (7) settled midfield in the run and boxed on to finish there when 4th (24.33) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Has winning claims on his best figures. PAW RAZOR (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (22.71) in a Grade 5 at Warrnambool. Key runner on best form. PAW ENNA (3) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Jed's Memory (24.37) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to give a sight. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Expecting another good run. MORAINE BLUEY (1) was in the money last start at this track and distance - poses a threat again.",
